snippet.title: Cityscapes: Sim Builder Gameplay Video - Apple Arcade
snippet.description:
A first look at Cityscapes: Sim Builder, a new city-building management strategy game from several former developers of SimCity. It's exclusive to the Apple Arcade subscription service.

#CityscapesSimBuilder #AppleArcade
